settings.announcement_text: Fast shipping • Easy install • Secure checkout
settings.hero_heading: Stop drops from disappearing between your seat and console.
settings.hero_subhead: A low-profile seat-gap filler that helps block everyday item drops and reduces distraction while driving.
settings.trust_line_1: Clear fit notes before purchase to reduce mismatch returns.
settings.trust_line_2: Seatbelt path should remain unobstructed when positioned correctly.

settings.bridge_point_2: Installs in under a minute per seat
settings.benefits_heading: Why people buy this first (and keep it)
settings.benefit_2: Simple fit around seat belt latch
settings.benefit_3: Looks clean and blends with interior

settings.benefit_6: Simple upgrade with high everyday utility
settings.ugc_subhead: Use approved uploads or source links only. Keep clips realistic and fit-focused.
settings.ugc_caption_1: No more phone/keys falling between seats.
settings.fit_body: Please check your seat-console gap shape and buckle position before ordering. This helps prevent mismatch returns.
settings.fit_dimensions:
Length: ~17.5 in (44.5 cm)
Gap depth support: typical front-seat gaps
Material: flexible PU/leather-like exterior (varies by supplier lot)
settings.fit_compatibility:
Works best with standard center-console seat gaps.
Best results when gap geometry is consistent from front to back.
settings.fit_exclusions:
Not ideal for extra-wide console gaps or very tight custom interiors.
Check seat movement and buckle clearance after install.
If between fit outcomes, order one set first.
settings.fit_reassurance: If fit is your top concern, review dimensions and the install clips before checkout.
settings.offer_subhead: Simple quantity-based packs. No confusing option trees.
settings.pack_2_sub: Best for two front seats / two vehicles
settings.offer_note: Expectation note: 1-Pack equals one unit quantity of this product in cart. Confirm your exact product contents and seat count before ordering.
settings.included_intro: Package contents depend on your selected product and quantity. Confirm this section matches your product listing details.
settings.included_item_1: Car seat gap filler unit(s) based on selected quantity
settings.included_item_5: Support access if fit questions come up
settings.shipping_text: Tracked shipping with delivery estimates shown at checkout.
settings.returns_text: Simple return policy with clear steps if your order isn’t a fit.
settings.support_text: Need fit help before ordering? Send your car make/model/year and a seat-gap photo for a better pre-purchase check.
settings.guarantee_text: If something arrives damaged or incorrect, contact support for a quick resolution.
